# Both Vercel projects deploy from this single repo:
#   - the dashboard project (Root Directory = dashboard)
#   - the backend project  (Root Directory = repo root, api/index.py)
# A repo-root .vercelignore is applied to BOTH, so it must NOT exclude
# dashboard/ — doing so empties the dashboard build. Keep this to backend-only
# cruft that is safe to drop from either upload.
data/
tests/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
